@startuml
' --- 時序圖 (整體程式) ---

== 遊戲啟動階段 ==

Player -> Game: 執行 main()
activate Game

Game -> Game: loadGameFromText()
activate Game

alt 存檔存在
    Game -> SaveFile: 讀取存檔
    SaveFile --> Game: 角色資料 (CSV格式)
    Game -> CPlayer: new C_Player(name, level, hp, mp)
    activate CPlayer
    CPlayer -> CPlayer: 計算屬性
    deactivate CPlayer
    Game --> Game: 返回 C_Player 物件
else 無存檔
    Game --> Game: 返回 null
    Game -> Player: 顯示「請輸入姓名」
    Player -> Game: 輸入名稱
    Game -> CPlayer: new C_Player(name)
    activate CPlayer
    CPlayer -> CPlayer: 初始化預設屬性
    deactivate CPlayer
end
deactivate Game

== 主遊戲迴圈 ==

loop 遊戲進行中
    Game -> Player: 顯示選單 (1.戰鬥 2.休息 3.狀態 4.離開)
    Player -> Game: 選擇選項

    alt 1. 選擇戰鬥
        Game -> Game: battle()
        note right: 參考「戰鬥流程」時序圖

    else 2. 選擇休息
        Game -> CPlayer: recover()
        activate CPlayer
        CPlayer -> CPlayer: 恢復滿血滿真氣
        deactivate CPlayer

    else 3. 選擇狀態
        Game -> CPlayer: 獲取各項數值 (HP/MP/ATK)
        CPlayer --> Game: 回傳資料
        Game -> Player: 顯示角色狀態視窗

    else 4. 選擇離開
        Game -> Game: saveGameAsText(s_player)
        activate Game
        Game -> CPlayer: 讀取當前屬性
        CPlayer --> Game: 名稱/等級/HP/MP
        Game -> SaveFile: 寫入 CSV 格式資料
        SaveFile --> Game: 存檔完成
        deactivate Game
        Game -> Player: 顯示「存檔完成，再見！」
        Game -> Game: 結束遊戲 (break)
    end
end

deactivate Game
@enduml